### Create a todo via MCP
POST http://localhost:8081/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Create a todo for buying groceries with description 'Buy milk, eggs, and bread'",
  "sessionId": "test-session-1"
}

### List all todos via MCP
POST http://localhost:8081/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me all my todos",
  "sessionId": "test-session-1"
}

### Complete a todo via MCP
POST http://localhost:8081/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Mark the groceries todo as completed",
  "sessionId": "test-session-1"
}

### Complex query via MCP
POST http://localhost:8081/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How many incomplete todos do I have? List them.",
  "sessionId": "test-session-1"
}
